                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/notif_text"
                    android:layout_width="0dp"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginStart="4dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="8dp"
                    android:layout_marginEnd="4dp"
                    android:layout_marginBottom="8dp"
                    android:gravity="center_horizontal"
                    android:text="An opportunity for students across the nation to become a part of the EFFERVESCENCE  family, IIIT Allahabad and bridge the sea of oblivion between IIIT Allahabad and your campus as you get familiar with the imbibing culture and scintillating ambience in our festivals.
As a Campus Ambassador, you would be the representative of IIIA in your college campus to spread awareness about EFFERVESCENCE and its glory through social media marketing etc.
Campus Ambassador registration is a chance for all of you to get involved in committed networking and get a glimpse of the corporate world, as you gain skills like team management, event organization, public speaking, social media, content writing and promotion and various other technical skills.
Bag this moment and register by associating with us as College Ambassador and we can together fashion out an ever splendid and grand
EFFERVESCENCE 2021."
                    android:textAlignment="center"
                    android:textColor="@color/baseTextPara"
                    app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
                    app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
                    app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias="0.5"
                    app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
                    app:layout_constraintTop_toBottomOf="@+id/textView2" />
            </androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout>
